works.complaint:
Hello,

We have made two previous complaints about this blogger who has launched a
 
personal attack on Baylissa Frederick, our Recovery Road founder and
author  
of the Recovery and Renewal book. We believe that her behavior has now  
become consistent with cyber bullying. We know that Blogger may not have a
 
policy on this and appreciate if this is the case. However, we are  
concerned for the welfare of Baylissa as this woman is now stalking her  
online, digging up old information, some which Baylissa was not aware of  

and which had her personal, private details such as her date of birth,  
phone number, etc. Everything we have found has or is being removed  
including photographs but is there any way of stopping this or can you
help  
us in any way?
